1. Build the Micro Server image:

    $ ./build_striped_micro_server.sh

2. Create a directory somewhere with configuration files for the Micro Server. It must include:

   job_server.yaml - Job Server configuration
   worker_master.yaml - Worker Master configuration
   
   Use templates found under micro_server/config
    
3. Run the micro_server:

    $ ./run_micro_server.sh -c /path/to/config_directory
    
4. Configure your client to talk to the Micro Server - use striped.yaml template found under test_job.

5. pip install striped

6. Run your client job. 

    


